An application which shows
how to use the TSmtpCli object to send
EMail on the Internet using the SMTP
protocol (used by every ISP). The
component is compatible with all Delphi
and all C++Builder versions.
The author can be contacted
at francois.piette@pophost.eunet.be. 
Updates can be found at 
http://www.rtfm.be/fpiette.
Unzip using the -d option to restore
directory tree. 
Freeware with full source code.
